\c 96
\s UNkulunkulu uyiN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 1 Hlabelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1 Lan. 16.23-33. Hlab. 98.\x*\x + Hlab. 92.9.\x* ingoma entsha\x + Hlab. 33.3.\x*; hlabelelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, mhlaba wonke\x + Hlab. 92.9.\x*.
\v 2 Hlabelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lidumise ibizo layo, litshumayele usindiso lwayo insuku ngensuku.
\v 3 Landisani udumo lwayo phakathi kwezizwe, izimangaliso zayo phakathi kwabantu bonke.
\v 4 Ngoba yinkulu iN\nd kosi\nd*, ifanele ukudunyiswa kakhulu, yona iyesabeka phezu kwabonkulunkulu bonke\x + Hlab. 48.1.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba bonke onkulunkulu bezizwe bayizithombe; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza amazulu.
\v 6 Ubukhosi lenkazimulo kuphambi kwayo, amandla\x + Hlab. 78.61.\x* lobuhle kusendlini yayo engcwele\x + Hlab. 78.61.\x*.
\v 7 Inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd*, zizukulwana zezizwe\x + Hlab. 22.27.\x*, inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd* udumo lamandla\x + Hlab. 92.9.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd* udumo lwebizo layo\x + Hlab. 92.9.\x*; lethani umnikelo\x + Hlab. 92.9.\x*, lingene emagumeni ayo\x + Hlab. 116.19.\x*.
\v 9 Ikhonzeni iN\nd kosi\nd* ebuhleni bobungcwele; lithuthumele phambi kwayo, mhlaba wonke\x + Hlab. 114.7.\x*.
\v 10 Tshonini phakathi kwezizwe: IN\nd kosi\nd* iyabusa\x + Hlab. 93.1. Hlab. 10.6.\x*. Lomhlaba umisiwe, kawuyikunyikinyeka\x + Hlab. 93.1. Hlab. 10.6.\x*; izabahlulela abantu\x + 96.13. Hlab. 58.11.\x* ngokuqonda\x + Hlab. 9.8.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Kawathokoze amazulu, lomhlaba ujabule; kaluhlokome ulwandle lokugcwala kwalo\x + Hlab. 97.1.\x*.
\v 12 Iganga kalithabe lakho konke okukulo\x + Isa. 35.1.\x*. Khona izihlahla zonke zegusu zizahlabela ngentokozo\x + 1 Lan. 16.33.\x*
\v 13 phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba iyeza, ngoba iyeza ukwahlulela umhlaba\x + 96.13. Hlab. 58.11.\x*; izakwahlulela umhlaba ngokulunga, labantu ngeqiniso layo\x + Hlab. 92.9.\x*.
